<p>Well he was alive long before there was a soviet union. He'd have to be around&#8230;say 30-35 when the &quot;secret missions&quot; happened, and that was very late 50s or very early 60s. As to the mythology, astronauts are smart! He probably went to college. Since we don't actually have any evidence he even existed, I took some liberties giving him a knack for myths. And since the lost cosmonaut theory is just a conspiracy theory, I had no problem saying, &quot;Screw it, they gave him an extra cool version of the suit for this secret mission.&quot;</p>

